solution:
The triangle is shown below:

[asy]
pair A,B,C;
A = (0,0);
B = (10,0);
C = (10,15);
draw(A--B--C--A);
draw(rightanglemark(C,B,A,26));
label("$A$",A,SW);
label("$B$",B,SE);
label("$C$",C,N);
